overview: Two of CF's most popular young studs, Dawson and Lucas, jetted off to Australia for a couple weeks of awesome fun! Their trip was jampacked full of adventure, including an exhilarating hot air balloon ride, an exciting helicopter flight, and treks through the streets of Sydney and Melbourne! Plus, of course, they had loads of intense sex!  Fortunately for us, Corbin followed along with his hand-held video camera and captured all of the hot action on tape!
title: Lucas & Dawson Down Under
